  "texts": [
    "In another case, artificial aromas could be used to mask spoilage, misleading consumers about product freshness and safety.",
    "These applications pose serious ethical questions about informed consumption and the potential erosion of consumer autonomy.",
    "To address these risks, regulatory agencies and industry bodies should establish ethical standards that govern how AI-generated flavors and scents may be deployed.",
    "These standards should require clear labeling, pre-market testing, and disclosure of whether sensory attributes are synthetically generated.",
    "The safety of AI-designed products must also be rigorously evaluated."
